50|$|The Poladha (alternatively Polada, Fuladi, Puladi) are a <b>Hazara</b> tribe {{found in}} Afghanistan, of the Southern branch of <b>Hazara.</b> Per several references, the Poladha {{are among the}} eight {{overarching}} <b>Hazara</b> tribes.|$|R
